  "detailed_description": "Follow Ana, a Human from Earth who wakes up in a strange place. After her vision comes in to focus, she realizes she's in a cell in an alien environment. With no one in sight, she decides to escape and try to return home.<br><br>As you tread through each room trying to find a way out, you learn that some rooms are trapped, but which is safe and which isn't? Can you spot/identify which room is trapped? If not, will the trap kill you or simply mess with you? Can you escape the maze or be Trapped Within?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/617230/extras/80e2e9f0d0224c44802780bed0d6db5c.avif?t=1666202338\" width=540 height=380 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/617230/extras/8379af6d75c39647a0d986cc8f3a3372.avif?t=1666202338\" width=540 height=380 /></span>",
